{"tid":2252660,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"柴灣山徑發現約400粒子彈殼","createTime":"2020-10-21T15:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T16:17:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cf68edd2230ab2d9d639ce769d830d231f5c20e9","tid":2252660,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"下午3時許，警方接獲報案，指有人在柴灣港島林道近美景路段一山坡發現一批子彈殼。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，於上址發現約400粒懷疑二戰時期子彈殼，已撿走化驗。案件列彈藥發現，交由柴灣分區人員跟進。案件中無須疏散，無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201021/RKNLAPYN4FHYDDPIW7YV7VARTQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201021%2FRKNLAPYN4FHYDDPIW7YV7VARTQ%2F&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=a93372f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201021%2FRKNLAPYN4FHYDDPIW7YV7VARTQ%2F&h=72b7dcec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201021/RKNLAPYN4FHYDDPIW7YV7VARTQ/</a>"},{"pid":"900d0de95ef6c7f6c1916686dd77d4483cbe095c","tid":2252660,"uid":251732,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47c0226a09d08b3bdd47d8086f33e6799e9b58c","tid":2252660,"uid":76804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:17:59.000Z","msg":"班狗諗住插贓嫁禍留低左就扮係二戰彈殼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61eec0ab541d31d8f6ad9e87a1b6eab7a7ebef3","tid":2252660,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf5fa97abf8ab7ca59038ee707f53c729eb6007","tid":2252660